data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!    This meticulously maintained 3 bed/ 2.5 bath townhome in highly sought after community of Montclair has it all. Downstairs there's a spacious dining room/living room combo with sleek tile flooring, a powder room, and kitchen complete with updated stainless steel appliances (2021), marble countertops and custom backsplash.    Upstairs, there is the master suite with a fully updated bathroom complete with a freestanding tub and glass enclosed shower, 2 guest bedrooms, guest bath, laundry room, and a large loft space that could be used as a second living room.    Some other features include new paint (2022), new garage door motor (2023), impact windows.
